\
Technical Details: Both CORAL award\'92s announced IBM Power Architecture, NVIDIA\'92s Volta GPU and Mellanox\'92s Interconnected technologies to advance key research initiatives. Oakridge\'92s new system Summit, is expected to perform atleast five times the present system Titan. Livermore\'92s new supercomputer,Sierra, is expected to perform atlas seven times faster than the present current LLNL\'92s Sequia.\
Argonne is yet to announce its CORAL award.\
